Story Statement

As a user, I want to see the Durood clearly displayed on my screen, so I can recite it comfortably while keeping track of tasbih counts below.

UI / UX Specifications
Durood Display Card

Position: Centered in the top half of the screen.

Shape: Rounded rectangle (radius 20px).

Background: Soft off-white (#FAFAFA).

Shadow: Subtle (2px blur, light gray #E0E0E0).

Padding: 20px inside.

Text:

Content: Only the Arabic Durood.

Font: Default app font.

Size: 24px.

Color: Black (#000000).

Alignment: Centered.